  "prompt": "What is Yelp?",
  "response": "Yelp is a popular online platform that allows users to find and review local businesses, such as restaurants, shops, services, and more. Founded in 2004, Yelp enables users to search for businesses based on various criteria, including location, type of service, and user ratings. \n\nUsers can write reviews, rate their experiences, upload photos, and provide tips about the businesses they've visited. Yelp also features a business owner section, where businesses can claim their listings, respond to reviews, update their information, and engage with customers. The platform serves as a valuable resource for consumers looking for trusted recommendations and helps businesses increase their visibility and attract customers. Additionally, Yelp offers various features like reservations, takeout, and delivery services through partnerships with other companies.",
